snippet.title: LMHPOLY
snippet.description:
This YouTube Channel is for Video Game Artists and CG Fanatics. For people who are interested in making Games, Game Assets, and CG Art in general. Here, you can find Video Tutorials, Tips and Tricks, the process of making Game Assets, and a lot of Cool Stuff made by me.

Mostly I make video tutorials for Blender and Unity.
